    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "An exceptional driver\u2019s example of the E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This unit is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for precise power delivery. Mechanically sound, the vehicle has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including Vanos calibration and subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension geometry remains true, offering the communicative feedback these chassis are known for. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its age, its mechanical integrity and drivetrain response are sharp, making it a prime candidate for the spirited purist.",
