    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously cared-for premium sedan that strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only the minor road nicks one would expect from a well-loved vehicle. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the leather upholstery is supple with no tears, and every button and electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is sound. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent synthetic oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection just completed. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are imperceptible, and the tires have plenty of tread remaining for the seasons ahead. It drives straight and quiet, reflecting a history of responsible ownership and garage-kept storage. This is an honest, reliable vehicle for a buyer who values quality and comfort. Includes two sets of keys, all-weather floor mats, and a complete folder of service records for your peace of mind.",
      "price": 31500.0,
