    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Are you looking for a reliable, well-loved ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? This car has been my trusty companion and is still in wonderful shape for its next owner. It runs super smoothly and I've made sure to keep up with the basics so it's ready to hit the road the moment you hop in. It\u2019s got that perfect balance of being dependable while still looking sharp in the driveway. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I\u2019d love for it to go to a great new home. Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
